fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:52): create a class "Action" that can do anything on your application.
fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:52): and do every call through one of these Actions.
fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:52): and keep a log of them...
fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:53): but that's probably an overkill for a simple application. :>
fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:54): an easier approach would be an 1 depth undo...
fb4f63345c7eea91488b2f1a957b138d (14:54): every call you make knows what to do to undo itself and registers that as the undo option...
